":17290,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/24\/prophet-meets-ibrahim-isra\/","url_meta":{"origin":37922,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ibrahim: The Prophet meets Abraham in Heaven","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI met Abraham on the night of my Ascension and he said: O Muhammad, greet your nation with peace from me. Tell them Paradise has pure soil and delicious water, that it is a level plain\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":927,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/18\/yusuf-ihsan-deen-fiqh\/","url_meta":{"origin":37922,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fiqh: Excellence in Islam requires understanding","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: It was said to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhich people are the most noble?'' The Prophet said, \u201cThe most noble to Allah are the most righteous.\u201d They said, \u201cThat is not what we are asking about.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe most noble of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34747,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/22\/khalil-ibrahim-generosity\/","url_meta":{"origin":37922,"position":4},"title":"Yusuf on Khalil: Ibrahim was Alla